OL,3,CJersey could become 'first Channel
OL,4,CIsland to enshrine the rights of same-
OL,5,Csex parents in law'
OL,7,FA law has been lodged in Jersey which
OL,8,Fmeans same-sex parents will have the
OL,9,Fsame legal rights as mixed-sex parents.
OL,11,FThe law will include a provision for
OL,12,Facquiring legal parental status and
OL,13,Fresponsibility and will be debated on
OL,14,F6 February 2024.
OL,16,FThe change is in line with Jersey's
OL,17,Fcommitment to upholding the United
OL,18,FNations Convention on the Rights of
OL,19,Fthe Child.
